queries.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) AS `numrows` FROM ( SELECT `tb1`.`id` FROM `products` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `product_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb2`.`product_id` INNER JOIN `product_catalogue_product` as `tb3` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb3`.`product_id` WHERE `deleted_at` = 0 GROUP BY `tb1`.`id` ) CI_count_all_results

SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb1`.`lft`, `tb1`.`rgt`, `tb1`.`image`, `tb2`.`canonical`, `tb2`.`title`, ( SELECT COUNT(p.id) FROM products as p JOIN product_catalogue_product as pcp ON pcp.product_id = p.id WHERE pcp.product_catalogue_id IN ( SELECT pc.id FROM product_catalogues as pc WHERE pc.lft >= tb1.lft AND pc.rgt <= tb1.rgt ) ) as totalProduct FROM `product_catalogues` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `product_catalogue_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb2`.`product_catalogue_id` WHERE `tb1`.`deleted_at` = 0 AND `tb1`.`id` IN ('9','2','3','4','5','6','7','8','9') ORDER BY `id` desc

SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb1`.`catalogueid`, `tb1`.`parentid`, `tb1`.`lft`, `tb1`.`rgt`, `tb1`.`level`, `tb1`.`order`, `tb2`.`title`, `tb2`.`objectid`, `tb2`.`canonical`, `tb2`.`catalogueid` as `dataid`, `tb1`.`type` FROM `menu` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `menu_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb2`.`objectid` AND `tb2`.`language` = '2' ORDER BY `order` desc
